<DialogueTree xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
              xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Outer-Wilds-New-Horizons/new-horizons/main/NewHorizons/Schemas/dialogue_schema.xsd">
    <NameField>Dace</NameField>

    <DialogueNode>
        <Name>Start</Name>
        <EntryCondition>DEFAULT</EntryCondition>
        <Dialogue>
            <Page>这些厚厚的云层遮住了所有的星星！</Page>
        </Dialogue>
        <DialogueOptionsList>
            <DialogueOption>
                <Text>不过你还是能听到信号吧！</Text>
                <DialogueTarget>Signals</DialogueTarget>
            </DialogueOption>
            <DialogueOption>
                <Text>你为什么要找星星呢？</Text>
                <DialogueTarget>Why</DialogueTarget>
            </DialogueOption>
        </DialogueOptionsList>
    </DialogueNode>

    <DialogueNode>
        <Name>Signals</Name>
        <Dialogue>
            <Page>我知道，但我听到的都是无聊的无线电信号！我想看星星！</Page>
        </Dialogue>
    </DialogueNode>

    <DialogueNode>
        <Name>Why</Name>
        <Dialogue>
            <Page>因为它们很酷！而且我已经看腻了无聊的云朵。</Page>
        </Dialogue>
    </DialogueNode>
</DialogueTree>